02:52.297 --> 02:53.715
What's that all about?

02:53.757 --> 02:55.884
A little something

02:53.757 --> 02:55.884
to remember me by.

02:55.926 --> 02:57.594
You know, it just

02:55.926 --> 02:57.594
occurred to me

02:57.636 --> 03:00.221
that we have not been apart

02:57.636 --> 03:00.221
for one night in 18 years.

03:00.263 --> 03:01.640
You gonna be

03:00.263 --> 03:01.640
