03:11.274 --> 03:13.276
Ten-hut!

03:11.274 --> 03:13.276
Well, Cadet,

03:13.318 --> 03:15.821
I see you survived.

03:13.318 --> 03:15.821
Yes, sir.

03:15.863 --> 03:17.405
I brought you

03:15.863 --> 03:17.405
a little something

03:17.447 --> 03:19.867
to take your mind

03:17.447 --> 03:19.867
