03:19.908 --> 03:21.743
This is a good

03:19.908 --> 03:21.743
opportunity for you

03:21.785 --> 03:23.453
to catch up

03:21.785 --> 03:23.453
on your homework.

03:23.495 --> 03:25.246
Take it from me--

03:25.288 --> 03:28.125
a lengthy hospital stay

03:25.288 --> 03:28.125
is the perfect environment

03:28.167 --> 03:31.461
to focus your mind and attack

03:28.167 --> 03:31.461
weaknesses in your character.

03:31.503 --> 03:33.254
If it hadn't been

03:31.503 --> 03:33.254
for this,

03:33.296 --> 03:36.216
I never would've learned

03:33.296 --> 03:36.216
conversational French.

03:37.551 --> 03:39.511
Carry on.

03:41.304 --> 03:43.182
Sorry, man.

03:43.223 --> 03:45.266
I was this close

03:43.223 --> 03:45.266
to going medieval on him.

03:45.308 --> 03:46.643
You feeling okay?

03:46.685 --> 03:49.270
I feel like I have a belly

03:46.685 --> 03:49.270
full of broken glass.

03:49.312 --> 03:52.273
Every time I breathe in, I

03:49.312 --> 03:52.273
almost pass out from the pain.

03:52.315 --> 03:54.193
This is the single

03:52.315 --> 03:54.193
greatest thing

03:54.234 --> 03:55.861
that has ever

03:54.234 --> 03:55.861
happened to me.

03:55.903 --> 03:58.279
What?

03:55.903 --> 03:58.279
Well, for as long

03:55.903 --> 03:58.279
as I can remember,

03:58.321 --> 04:00.365
my mom has been

03:58.321 --> 04:00.365
torturing me with guilt.

04:00.407 --> 04:03.660
I've never been able to fight

04:00.407 --> 04:03.660
back, but this is perfect.

04:03.702 --> 04:08.123
Her first-born child almost dies

04:03.702 --> 04:08.123
a thousand miles from home,

04:08.165 --> 04:10.125
and she's the one

04:08.165 --> 04:10.125
who sent me here.

04:10.167 --> 04:12.920
She can't dismiss it,

04:10.167 --> 04:12.920
she can't argue about it,

04:12.961 --> 04:15.005
she can't twist it around

04:12.961 --> 04:15.005
and make it my fault.

04:15.047 --> 04:16.339
It's beautiful.

04:16.381 --> 04:18.884
(groans)

04:16.381 --> 04:18.884
Dude, you almost died.

04:18.926 --> 04:21.302
I want you to say that

04:18.926 --> 04:21.302
again when she gets here.

04:21.344 --> 04:24.556
Oh, this poor woman has no

04:21.344 --> 04:24.556
idea what she's walking into.

04:25.724 --> 04:27.308
Okay, Mom's only gonna be gone

04:27.350 --> 04:30.311
for about four or five days,

04:27.350 --> 04:30.311
