05:09.392 --> 05:11.394
For crying out loud.

05:11.436 --> 05:13.354
Be strong.

05:15.023 --> 05:16.399
Lois will get through

05:15.023 --> 05:16.399
her operation.

05:16.441 --> 05:17.818
