05:17.859 --> 05:19.611
No, no, Craig,

05:17.859 --> 05:19.611
it was Francis.

05:19.653 --> 05:21.362
Oh, my God.

05:21.404 --> 05:22.656
Did he shoot her?

05:22.697 --> 05:23.824
I knew it.

05:23.865 --> 05:26.243
I t-told her

05:23.865 --> 05:26.243
to stay away from him.

05:26.285 --> 05:28.245
That boy has been

05:26.285 --> 05:28.245
nothing but trouble.

05:28.287 --> 05:31.206
Uh, Craig, uh, Lois did

05:28.287 --> 05:31.206
not have an operation.

05:31.248 --> 05:32.874
