05:49.516 --> 05:51.392
Or maybe you could,

05:51.434 --> 05:54.896
I don't know, shut up about

05:51.434 --> 05:54.896
your mom for half a second.

05:54.938 --> 05:56.773
No one's that bad.

05:56.815 --> 05:59.484
Hey, I been sugar-coating it

05:56.815 --> 05:59.484
