06:06.741 --> 06:09.410
(weakly): You think that's

06:06.741 --> 06:09.410
gonna appease your guilt?

06:09.452 --> 06:10.620
What guilt?

06:10.662 --> 06:12.622
Boy, it's stuffy in here.

06:12.664 --> 06:14.833
That can't be good for you.

06:14.875 --> 06:16.084
You look pasty.

06:16.126 --> 06:17.669
Have you had a

06:16.126 --> 06:17.669
bowel movement?

06:17.711 --> 06:19.796
When is the last time

06:17.711 --> 06:19.796
you moved your bowels?

06:17.711 --> 06:19.796
Mom...

06:19.838 --> 06:21.006
Hello.

06:21.048 --> 06:22.924
Who are you?

06:22.966 --> 06:25.844
Edwin Spangler-- I am commandant

06:22.966 --> 06:25.844
of Marlin Academy.

06:25.886 --> 06:27.888
Good for you.

06:27.929 --> 06:29.681
Where's your eye?

06:29.723 --> 06:30.682
Pardon?

06:30.724 --> 06:32.351
Do your ears work?

06:32.391 --> 06:34.144
Do you have some business

06:32.391 --> 06:34.144
with my son?

06:34.186 --> 06:35.687
He needs to rest.

06:35.729 --> 06:38.439
Well, I stopped by to pick up

06:35.729 --> 06:38.439
your boy's homework.

06:38.481 --> 06:40.525
Homework?! You're not

06:38.481 --> 06:40.525
giving him homework.

06:40.567 --> 06:42.236
My son nearly

06:40.567 --> 06:42.236
lost his life--

06:42.277 --> 06:43.862
something that never

06:42.277 --> 06:43.862
would've happened

06:43.904 --> 06:46.156
if you'd taken proper care

06:43.904 --> 06:46.156
of him in the first place.

06:46.198 --> 06:47.949
Well, I assure you, ma'am,

06:47.991 --> 06:50.702
had it not been for Francis's

06:47.991 --> 06:50.702
long history of crying wolf...

06:50.744 --> 06:52.371
Crying wolf?

06:52.411 --> 06:53.663
You listen to me, you idiot!

06:53.705 --> 06:55.456
My child is sick.

06:55.498 --> 06:58.085
He does not need you

06:55.498 --> 06:58.085
marching in here, puffing up

06:58.126 --> 07:00.461
your little chest

06:58.126 --> 07:00.461
and making his life

07:00.503 --> 07:02.547
more miserable

07:00.503 --> 07:02.547
than it already is.

07:02.589 --> 07:04.465
Why don't you just go play

07:02.589 --> 07:04.465
army man somewhere else?

07:12.432 --> 07:15.435
God, she is magnificent.

07:18.563 --> 07:20.982
Dude, your mom rocks.

07:25.737 --> 07:27.572
(sighs)

07:27.614 --> 07:29.532
(whimpers)

07:38.166 --> 07:40.419
Hmm.

07:46.383 --> 07:48.468
(sighs)

07:51.763 --> 07:53.514
MAN (over TV):

07:51.763 --> 07:53.514
You got a girl, Rizzo?

07:53.556 --> 07:54.933
RIZZO: Yeah, Sarge.

07:53.556 --> 07:54.933
