08:06.653 --> 08:09.530
between speed  and  torque.

08:09.572 --> 08:11.116
This is great.

08:11.158 --> 08:13.452
I can make a huge mess,

08:11.158 --> 08:13.452
build a killer robot,

08:13.493 --> 08:15.329
and Mom's not here

08:13.493 --> 08:15.329
to yell at us.

08:15.370 --> 08:17.538
